      "text": "まいったな……まさかドッキリ番組から\n千紗にオファーがくるとは……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh no… I can't believe an offer came for Chisa from a prank show…\nI never thought she'd get an offer like this…",
        "id": ""
