    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_05_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_05_01-chs001.m4a",
      "text": "おはようございます、{user}さん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good morning‚ {user}-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_05_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_05_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "（しかも「ホラー好きを公言するアイドルは）\n（本当に幽霊を怖がらないのか」検証する企画って……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(And it's a segment about)\n(\"Can an idol who claims to love horror really not be scared by ghosts?\"…)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_05_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_05_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "（ようは千紗に心霊ドッキリを仕掛けて）\n（怖がらせるってことだよな？）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(In other words‚ they're planning to set up a supernatural prank on Chisa…)\n(To scare her‚ right?)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_05_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_05_01-chs002.m4a",
      "text": "……{user}さん？\nあれ、おかしいな。聞こえてるよね……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…{user}-san?\nHuh‚ that's strange. You can hear me‚ right…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_05_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_05_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "（番組スタッフは、どんなにホラー好きでも実際に）\n（恐怖体験をすれば怖がると思っているようだが……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(Even though the program staff might believe that even a horror enthusiast…)\n(Will get scared when actually facing a fearful experience…)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_05_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_05_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "（千紗のホラー耐性は筋金入りだ）\n（全然怖がらなくて番組が成り立たない可能性も……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(Chisa's resistance to horror is solid.)\n(If she doesn't get scared at all‚ the show might not work…)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_05_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_05_01-chs003.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san!!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_05_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_05_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "うわぁっ！　びっくりした……なんだ、千紗か",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Whoa! You scared me… Oh‚ it's you‚ Chisa.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_05_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_05_01-chs004.m4a",
      "text": "びっくりしたのはこっちです\n無視されてるのかと思っちゃいました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I was the one surprised.\nI thought you were ignoring me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_05_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_05_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "あ……すまない、ちょっと考えごとをしていたんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah… Sorry‚ I was lost in thought for a moment.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.7333333333,
